text: Kanał is a 1956 Polish World War II drama movie directed by Andrzej Wajda and starring Teresa Iżewska, Tadeusz Janczar, Wieńczysław Gliński, Stanisław Mikulski, Emil Karewicz. This was the first movie of the "Three Wars" trilogy by director Andrzej Wajda. ==Other websites== * * Category:1956 drama movies Category:1956 war movies Category:World War II movies Category:Polish drama movies Category:Movies directed by Andrzej Wajda
title: Kanał
